"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 614px; height: 709px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     CBC: complete blood count; ESR: erythrocyte sedimentation rate; PPD: purified protein derivative test for tuberculosis.",
"     <br>",
"      * Empiric antibiotic therapy should include coverage for common pathogens such as group A streptococcus and",
